projectInfo.title: Delta Delta Delta
projectInfo.introduction: Tri-Delt Sorority was getting ready for spring with new Graphic Tees for their sisters. After designing, my job was to find the most cost-effective way to print these shirts, yet keeping the color scheme and cohesiveness of the design we approved.
